item.title: Help please
item.dc:creator: @Yz85Racer Yz85Racer
item.description:
@Yz85Racer wrote:

Right click my computer, click properties, and then click the advanced tab, then look for environmental viarables And go to system variables, click new, and set it out like this

Variable Name: CLASSPATH
Variable Value: .;C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_9\lib\ext\QTJava.zip

Then go to your server, and right click your compiler, and clcik edit, or open wit, then notepad, delete everything and repaste with this

@echo off COLOR 09 title YamahaScape Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\java.exe" server pause
